tags.name: CTI
tags.description: Control your desktop phone via our API. You can enable the CTI API in your [settings](https://web.placetel.de/settings/cti_api). These endpoints are only supported by Cisco desk phones. In order to consume events that happen on the phones and receive operation results, you need to register a [webhook subscription](/#Placetel-API-Subscriptions).
